data.description: If you're looking for a townhouse in Calera, AL, you're in luck! This townhome offers access to I-65, making it an easy commute to Birmingham or other nearby cities. This townhome is spacious and has 2 primary bedrooms upstairs with walk in closets! Laundry room is also located upstairs. It also has a private fenced backyard, perfect for entertaining or relaxing.
